Comment: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Flames
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:04.95,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let’s go to the arcade in front of the train station on the way home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.57,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,OK, sounds good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.24,0:01:47.13,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,1,2,3!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.74,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,1,2,3!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.35,0:01:55.01,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,1,2,3!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.70,0:01:56.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1,2!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.28,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.39,0:02:14.91,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.52,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we won’t be able to protect our strong reputation!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.60,0:02:22.41,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys going to make us seniors graduate in shame?!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.48,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kirioka, eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.62,0:02:29.75,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky him: getting a rugby scholarship to Jounan University.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.12,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Hey, look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.33,0:02:37.28,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu, eh? What’s he thinking?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.20,0:02:41.92,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Running around every day, even though he’s not in a club.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.78,0:02:48.72,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he’s creepy: he never says anything. He’s like a block of ice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.55,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.25,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu, you sure are popular!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.72,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.92,0:03:20.33,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we’re pretty bummed out right now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.68,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,for getting rejected from our first choice schools.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.75,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We’re borrowing you for a sec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.29,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,When you’re pissed off, beating the shit out of someone is a great relief!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.32,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.73,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.10,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Why not solve this with money?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.72,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,How about 50,000 yen ($350 USD) each?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.30,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,50,000?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.85,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll bring it tomorrow, so let me go. Please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.48,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, it’s so good...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.66,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the best!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.74,0:04:13.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.04,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.85,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. If it’s for you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.19,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But you must be the only high schooler in the country...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.77,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,who plays around with hostesses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.52,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I need 100,000.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.36,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You better not have found a girl.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.91,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,It’s for men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:43.32,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! Really? If you’re lying I’ll make you pay it back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:47.69,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Ryuu-chan, no. Oh, God...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.71,0:04:49.82,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.59,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:05:01.09,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. If you have any problems, talk to us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.20,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.35,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.52,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look, that’s the second year student (Junior) Naito Emi, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.92,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Her family is incredibly wealthy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.81,0:05:26.05,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, her family owns a huge hospital!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.29,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They even have two Mercedes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.08,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.81,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.39,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like to show my appreciation; are you free this Sunday?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.54,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.83,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go to the ocean, then?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.08,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.11,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll see you on Sunday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.41,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice person.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.19,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty with long hair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.19,0:06:34.55,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,But they make us tie it for school so...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.97,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You’re pretty with tied hair, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.89,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.89,0:06:56.40,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why do you run everyday?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.48,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Exams are coming up soon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.30,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,To keep my body in shape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.52,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I’ll walk you home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.52,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.01,0:07:18.10,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine, it’s right there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.43,0:07:24.21,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What a house...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.90,0:07:32.36,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for today, even walking me home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.71,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Will you see me again?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.71,0:07:38.70,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But... I’m so boring…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.95,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve always loved you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.87,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve always been looking only at you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.70,0:07:49.85,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.66,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,So will you see me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.20,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.76,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.65,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You’re late.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.38,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I was with a friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.77,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Choose your friends wisely...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.77,0:08:36.72,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,since your future is to marry a man who will take over the hospital.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.97,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.97,0:08:42.59,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not fair that brother got to become a lawyer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.93,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don’t bring me into this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.21,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Something wrong?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.43,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,That red mark on your neck...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.43,0:08:55.30,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh this? It’s nothing, I bumped it, so don’t worry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.30,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to my room now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.61,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Emi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.02,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuichi-san...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.85,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Misao, hurry, hurry, big news!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.39,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,What big news?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.66,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, isn’t that your brother?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.77,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,Brother…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.77,0:09:39.12,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But this is surprising, for your brother to have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.73,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he had no interest in girls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.97,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on, brother? Since when did you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.98,0:09:56.50,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Kirioka. Looks like your Madonna was taken by Kaizu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.60,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, brother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.21,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.24,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,Say, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.24,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.63,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, about your girlfriend...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.39,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuichi, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.82,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to grandpa’s house, are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.54,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t go; I have to study for exams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.81,0:10:31.71,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you’d say that. Have you decided on a college?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.77,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo University.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.43,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That will cost money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.43,0:10:39.97,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry. Plus, I’ll be going to a state school in two years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.51,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Give your mother an estimate of the costs later.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.84,0:10:44.90,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.55,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going. Misao, get ready.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.03,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,... yes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.15,0:11:00.08,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I never understand what he’s thinking!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.45,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.17,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,You mean brother?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.53,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don’t know if it’s that he lacks cuteness or whatever...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.53,0:11:10.71,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but he’s my child, yet I don’t feel like I want to do anything for him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.40,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Father.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.84,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,He has it rough these days, studying for college entrance exams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.65,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,We should warmly watch over him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.97,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.07,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.92,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody’s here, it’s all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.59,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go to my room.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.83,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... uh... sure, let’s!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.78,0:11:53.64,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s quite tidy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.82,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.80,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop! We can’t...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.49,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t! Stop it, we can’t!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.89,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.37,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, we can’t...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.17,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.50,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.87,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.02,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what’s with that on your neck?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.32,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nothing, don’t worry about it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.90,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, show me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.62,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, please. Let go of me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.71,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.44,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Father?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.12,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her neck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.97,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Emi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.81,0:13:13.37,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you won’t reveal his name?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.86,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,We love each other.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.76,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.01,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be foolish!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.01,0:13:23.43,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let some nobody we don’t even know take you from us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.81,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You are important to this family in finding an heir to the hospital!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.59,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s too late, I’m not a doll anymore...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.22,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,We've already slept together!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.32,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.54,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I have kiss marks...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.36,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,We love each other.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.12,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a woman...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.27,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.79,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Father, stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.12,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, let go of me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.60,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this man?!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:52.21,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Father, calm down, let me handle it. I want to discuss this with Emi alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.46,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I’ll let you handle this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.65,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine now. Are you hurt?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.49,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think I’ve done anything wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.82,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feelings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.91,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,But I would like to meet this person.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.00,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like I want to fight him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:18.48,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to get to know the person you fell in love with.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.40,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I’ll ask him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.73,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu Ryuuichi-kun, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.88,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You’re Emi-kun’s brother? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.53,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the thief?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.29,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Father, calm down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.70,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry about my father.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.70,0:14:50.09,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,He insisted on coming when he heard I was meeting you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.51,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.67,*Default,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, what would you like?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.93,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.09,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The same.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:07.21,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get to the point: I don’t want you near Emi from now on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.69,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be something like this, but I can’t promise that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.33,0:15:16.82,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.33,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You probably know this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.46,0:15:24.04,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,but my Father has planned for Emi’s husband to take over the hospital.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.20,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a Humanities student, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.56,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You have no interest in Medicine?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.92,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,No, I do not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.92,0:15:35.16,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But I am serious about Emi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.93,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.47,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that but… this is difficult...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:43.32,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No it isn’t, we just have to keep him away from Emi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.32,0:15:47.55,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,But Father, Emi is saying she would leave the house if she has to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.10,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t let her!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.10,0:15:52.47,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,So you won’t forgive us no matter what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.49,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.74,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,OK. I understand, we'll break up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.01,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.39,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But I have one condition.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.81,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Go ahead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.18,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Give me 10,000,000 yen ($7,000 USD).
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.57,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.75,0:16:14.42,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,10,000,000?! Are you… Serious?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.89,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I love her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.24,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But after hearing the realities of your family...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.24,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I am forcing myself to break up with her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.24,0:16:24.28,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I think I deserve compensation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.55,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of foolishness are you talking about?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.43,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You weren’t even married, what do you mean compensation? How dare you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.62,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to say that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.62,0:16:36.34,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I think if I tell her to leave your family, she will.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.15,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You... what kind of a man are you?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.15,0:16:43.59,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, think about it. I’m expecting a positive reply.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.78,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.46,0:16:51.16,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What a bastard! That’s a high school student?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.16,0:16:55.28,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Emi sure fell in love with a horrible man...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.90,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Father?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.97,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid. You think I’d believe a story like that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.97,0:17:07.41,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest. Ryuuichi-san isn’t a that kind of a person!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:11.22,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not lying; Toushiro heard it too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.48,0:17:16.09,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true, Kaizu Ryuuichi really asked for 10,000,000...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.59,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve lost my respect for you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.40,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Even you, brother. You said you were going alone...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.20,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,but you must have planned this story with father from the beginning!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.92,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, please believe us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.92,0:17:30.93,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, I don’t want to hear it anymore! I can’t believe you two!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.93,0:17:31.97,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Emi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.95,0:17:36.18,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, this is just as he planned!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.44,0:17:44.06,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Father. Solving this with money will only hurt Emi more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.82,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know, don’t worry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.24,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It’s 5,000,000. Now break up with her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.57,0:18:02.63,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you confused? I said 10,000,000.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.63,0:18:07.13,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The rest will be paid after you break up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.26,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I’ll trust you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.26,0:18:16.79,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But you understand what will happen if you betray me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.88,0:18:21.72,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and break up with her. That’s all you need to do!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.25,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, bye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.03,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t take it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.03,0:18:35.29,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,My father then says you asked for 10,000,000 yen to break up with me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.16,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.91,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for telling you this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.91,0:18:45.50,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe in you, so don’t worry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.22,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,It must be tough...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.87,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,for your family to worry about you this much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.92,0:18:53.90,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.90,0:18:57.85,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,We're just from different worlds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.85,0:19:02.84,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You should marry a doctor, for your own sake, as well as your family's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.84,0:19:05.96,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don’t say things like that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.09,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s break up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.93,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,If it's going to happen anyway then we should do it now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.59,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,before the pain becomes deeper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.46,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,No!! I don’t want that!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.74,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ryuuichi-san.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.23,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.11,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.81,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,frankly, I’ve grown tired of you, of your body too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.67,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.52,0:19:36.16,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,So let’s end it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.70,*Default,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.70,0:19:39.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.64,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.71,0:20:07.82,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Father!! Father!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.32,0:20:11.39,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly, Emi’s condition is strange!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.14,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Emi! Emi!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.96,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.63,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, I found this under her bed!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.59,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping pills! Call an ambulance now!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.70,*Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Father, you didn’t pay him?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.25,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, hurry!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.31,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Emi, don’t die!! Emi!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.31,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? Naito Emi tried to commit suicide?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.31,0:20:46.63,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but she survived. It was because she was dumped by Kaizu, apparently.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.35,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.66,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can’t believe it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.66,0:20:54.34,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there’s Kaizu! I can’t believe he came to school...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.61,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have no feelings?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.73,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.57,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu, come with me for a minute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.86,0:21:14.65,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Emi tried to kill herself?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.79,0:21:20.48,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that’s why everyone was looking at me strangely...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.48,0:21:24.50,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it? Don’t you feel the least bit sorry?!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.50,0:21:28.34,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, what do I care about people I’m no longer with?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.43,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,YOU BASTARD!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.75,0:21:36.04,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you getting mad?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.88,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. You liked Naito Emi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.88,0:21:43.12,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, I’m gonna teach you a lesson!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.98,0:21:48.22,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I should tell you about her body in return?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.74,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you bastard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.26,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin is pearly white, and her breasts are huge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.26,0:21:55.44,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!! I don’t want to hear about that!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.94,0:22:03.73,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,These are the punches of the best athlete in the district?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.96,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,What a mouth you have...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.96,0:22:11.02,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,say just one more thing and I’ll rip you apart!! Watch your back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.90,0:22:23.47,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on, Ryuuichi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.96,0:22:27.41,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You’re incredible today!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.86,0:22:44.27,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, put some medicine on it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.22,0:22:46.72,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.17,0:22:49.90,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll get infected.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.87,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I said it’s fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.70,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.34,0:22:59.10,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine, it’s fine like this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.18,0:23:09.42,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.50,0:23:13.51,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.51,0:23:19.15,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu-kun here is saying you assulted him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.24,0:23:21.65,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.90,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kirioka? You aren’t the type to do something like this, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.36,0:23:31.25,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it’s true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.42,0:23:32.68,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kirioka!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.92,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that’s most unfortunate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.92,0:23:37.60,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Unless there’s a good reason I have no choice. Kirioka-kun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.70,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,your scholarship to Jounan University will be revoked.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.65,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.91,0:23:49.80,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we can’t have violent students receiving scholarships.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.93,0:23:53.57,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kirioka, tell him! There must have been a reason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.57,0:23:55.67,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,To cause you to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.26,0:23:58.43,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.70,0:24:02.05,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.03,0:24:05.43,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t reveal that…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.92,0:24:08.74,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You may leave, Kaizu-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.33,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.26,0:24:25.70,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see Kaizu? Where’d he go?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.48,0:24:32.46,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaizu’s gonna get killed by Kirioka!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.55,0:24:35.61,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Should we save him and get more money?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.61,0:24:39.16,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! We can’t beat Kirioka.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.27,0:24:41.14,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then let’s go watch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.14,0:24:43.23,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let’s go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.72,0:24:45.85,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.22,0:24:52.80,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Losing your love, losing your scholarship...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.80,0:24:55.61,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,how pathetic can you get, Kirioka?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.73,0:24:58.53,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not afraid of anything now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.53,0:25:01.69,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the shit out of you, you bastard!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.66,0:25:13.90,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless. I've been able to see your punches from the start.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.07,0:25:16.36,*Default,Kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Then you... yesterday...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.51,0:25:18.48,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,This time I’ll attack.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.47,0:25:26.57,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Now get up, I’ll teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.28,0:25:28.59,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.02,0:25:36.42,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What're you lookin' at?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.36,0:25:38.34,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Er... um...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.34,0:25:42.79,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You’re strong. If you’re so strong why did you, against us...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.92,0:25:45.19,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I only solve things with money the first time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.33,0:25:48.51,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And I don’t like wasting my time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.93,0:26:22.40,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.28,0:26:24.61,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuichi!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.61,0:26:27.18,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I wrote it in the letter but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.18,0:26:28.78,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I got into my college...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.78,0:26:32.31,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,and I’m skipping the graduation ceremony to go to Tokyo with her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.31,0:26:37.18,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! We haven’t paid your school expenses yet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.23,0:26:40.12,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,How rude. Will you please shut up?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.12,0:26:41.33,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.41,0:26:44.84,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cut off my relationship with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.02,0:26:46.30,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuichi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.37,0:26:47.59,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.72,0:26:53.91,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I’ll pay for everything myself. I don’t need anything from you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.02,0:26:56.30,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You better not come back crying!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.30,0:27:00.57,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I cry? I’m happy to cut myself off from you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.99,0:27:02.32,*Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.57,0:27:06.48,*Default,Misao,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!! Brother!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.98,0:27:11.08,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me. Tell mom that too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.51,0:27:12.94,*Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Brother…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.08,0:27:15.17,*Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuichi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.45,0:27:23.19,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You’re free, Ryuuichi-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.19,0:27:25.24,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Parents don’t matter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.32,0:27:31.05,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’m taking on Tokyo. I don’t intend to ever return to this small town.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.28,0:27:34.28,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to become a first-rate hostess in Ginza.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.28,0:27:35.78,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do our best, Ryuuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.78,0:27:36.83,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.87,0:28:00.25,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you join anything?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.25,0:28:03.75,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about joining the tennis circle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.41,0:28:07.45,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they have connections to all-girl colleges...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.45,0:28:11.31,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and that the daughter of the head of Sumibishi Bank joined there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.37,0:28:12.73,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuichi!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.59,0:28:17.02,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuko...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.19,0:28:21.37,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. I know I’m not suppose to come...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.37,0:28:24.05,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,but just for today, forgive me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.13,0:28:26.85,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show off to everyone that my boyfriend goes to school here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.85,0:28:29.94,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,and that he’s this wonderfully gorgeous!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:30.20,0:28:31.38,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.46,0:28:34.19,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That’s why I love you!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.44,0:28:35.45,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ginza?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.45,0:28:37.93,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m off today. Hey, let's go somewhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.93,0:28:41.56,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Roppongi, Asobu, or Daikaiyama?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:54.99,0:28:58.60,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that’s the Sumibishi daughter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:05.85,0:29:10.89,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She’s cute, but it’s no good. She's outta our league.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.89,0:29:12.04,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.10,0:29:14.53,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But the older students are all around her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.53,0:29:19.05,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And look, older students have their eyes on all the other girls too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:21.93,0:29:27.95,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and do you know what guys call girls from each year?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.29,0:29:31.24,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,First years are snacks, Second years are prime meat...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.24,0:29:34.77,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,third years are old ladies, fourth years are just rotten.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.98,0:29:41.55,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So I’m an old lady, Kuroeda Kieko, third year. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.55,0:29:44.60,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, we would never call you an old lady, not at all...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.60,0:29:45.92,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s the captain!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.47,0:29:54.22,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He’s impressive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.59,0:29:57.09,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was good and works fast...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.09,0:30:00.64,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like the captain’s picked the Sumibishi daughter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.11,0:30:14.66,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.14,0:30:19.36,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always sleep around with men like this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.36,0:30:23.57,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time, because you were so sexy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:23.80,0:30:26.82,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be to make someone jealous?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.82,0:30:28.84,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be stupid!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.02,0:30:31.68,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my mood, I’m leaving.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.46,0:30:34.62,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.58,0:30:38.69,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty when you're angry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.18,0:30:52.54,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t feel this good with the captain!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.54,0:30:56.23,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible... so this is real sex...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.95,0:31:05.26,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroeda was?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.26,0:31:08.93,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was with a first year named Kaizu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.93,0:31:13.02,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t she your girlfriend? We can’t let the underclassmen do as they please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.02,0:31:15.38,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:17.82,0:31:19.14,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroeda-kun?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.14,0:31:23.38,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain, let me introduce you. This is first year student, Kaizu-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.38,0:31:24.52,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.52,0:31:25.87,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.48,0:31:31.23,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, what are you doing? With a first year?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.23,0:31:35.30,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,You were doing the same with the Sumibishi girl.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.56,0:31:37.54,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you’re jealous.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.54,0:31:39.69,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, don’t be so arrogant.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.69,0:31:40.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:40.71,0:31:43.86,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kuroeda-san, I’ll be over there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.06,0:31:47.21,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, I hear you’re really good at tennis.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.21,0:31:49.71,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’ve never played it before.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.02,0:31:51.14,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t lie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.14,0:31:52.66,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.75,0:31:54.93,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me test you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.93,0:31:57.62,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t bully him like that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.62,0:32:00.07,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way he could compete with you in tennis!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.07,0:32:02.61,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,You stay back. Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.62,0:32:11.00,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the captain is gonna play a newcomer!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.00,0:32:14.96,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really! Why? Must be a really good new student!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.96,0:32:17.51,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is the best player in this circle, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.51,0:32:18.51,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.10,0:32:25.65,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… where on the court should I stand?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.71,0:32:27.66,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t act stupid, here I go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.72,0:32:30.57,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Kaizu-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.19,0:32:36.10,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I’ll crush and embarrass him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.33,0:32:51.59,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this? He really can’t play, in that case...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.77,0:33:10.91,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this isn’t a good match at all. How boring!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:15.43,0:33:17.75,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough captain, stop!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.04,0:33:19.37,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,The poor guy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.01,0:33:27.78,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Not what I was expecting. Let’s go, Keiko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:36.00,0:33:37.84,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy, eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.12,0:33:42.62,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuko, can I have 30,000 yen ($210 USD)?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.79,0:33:44.15,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:44.15,0:33:47.66,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,To hire a tennis pro for some intensive training.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.81,0:33:53.06,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. I’m Kaizu, I called you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.22,0:33:54.68,*Default,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a tough teacher.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.68,0:33:57.05,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,That’s fine, thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.31,0:34:14.92,*Default,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve improved greatly, why don’t we rest?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.18,0:34:16.87,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:30.20,0:34:32.75,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So how’s practice going?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.21,0:34:38.70,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Sayuki, a 2nd year from Keizai University. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.76,0:34:43.79,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you don’t like shaking hands? No matter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:44.09,0:34:47.64,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have the perfect part-time job for you. Would you like to try it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.90,0:34:48.93,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,A job?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:49.13,0:34:52.26,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as a Black Suit in Roppongi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.60,0:34:53.95,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,A Black Suit...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.59,0:35:12.81,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They call the guys who work in the disco clubs “black suits”.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.01,0:35:16.93,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're a big part of the clubs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:17.22,0:35:20.03,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The crazy girls want to sleep with all of them...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.14,0:35:22.28,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and most places succeed or fail...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.28,0:35:23.94,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,depending on the skill of the black suits.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.10,0:35:26.42,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But I... can't do a job like that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.42,0:35:32.10,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fun, and a good study of society. And you’ll never run out of girls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.33,0:35:37.71,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel too that something is lacking in your school life?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.17,0:35:39.62,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.74,0:35:45.03,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The same type of people can recognize it, with intuition or whatever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.27,0:35:48.09,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun, let me give it a try.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.33,0:36:06.90,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You’re new, eh? Very cool, how about hanging out after work?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.02,0:36:33.65,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected, Tokyo is great!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.11,0:36:38.78,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is so exciting. This is the city for me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.09,0:36:42.20,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll become the top here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.24,0:36:46.11,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, what’s been going on lately?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.34,0:36:50.50,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You rarely come home, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.50,0:36:52.79,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Things are tough on first years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:52.79,0:36:55.66,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I have tennis practice, and a friend got me a part-time job.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.66,0:36:59.60,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!! You have a girl, don’t you? Say it!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.60,0:37:00.89,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. Let go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.89,0:37:02.59,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t take it, I’ll kill you!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.59,0:37:04.53,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.31,0:37:06.46,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.66,0:37:10.04,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough, stop complaining about my life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.19,0:37:13.05,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I’m leaving this house!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.28,0:37:16.35,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? Just try it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.35,0:37:18.74,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I’ll seriously kill you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.90,0:37:20.68,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,We’re finished.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.77,0:37:26.62,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I’m not your slave!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.84,0:37:28.76,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.99,0:37:30.24,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:30.80,0:37:31.86,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.93,0:37:39.47,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I’ll really kill you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.61,0:37:41.25,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be stupid!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.25,0:37:44.14,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious! I’ll kill you then myself!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.50,0:37:49.56,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.22,0:37:56.78,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,No... stop!! No!! Stop it!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.63,0:38:06.18,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t stop, Ryuuichi! I’ll do whatever you want!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.44,0:38:11.44,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t throw me away... please!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.67,0:38:35.25,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He came to the trip?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.25,0:38:38.73,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he’d quit the circle after losing to the captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.71,0:38:45.58,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s awesome! What kind of car is this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.73,0:38:50.20,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Mercedes-Benz 190SL. From about 30 years ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.43,0:38:53.36,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s you. How boring.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.36,0:38:56.20,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t want to ride in the car of a loser?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.20,0:38:57.72,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.85,0:39:04.53,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t want to ride around with such a boring, spoiled girl either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.82,0:39:08.61,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.81,0:39:16.84,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about what he says, he’s totally lame!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.55,0:39:22.83,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, looks like Kaizu’s gonna play the Captain again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.83,0:39:24.68,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He requested a game!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.74,0:39:28.75,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What an idiot, he’ll just get crushed again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:28.75,0:39:32.02,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun, I’m going to go watch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.73,0:39:46.17,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,You got a little better, eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.22,0:39:48.57,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I got a coach and practiced.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.72,0:39:54.16,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t see how you could improve too much in a month or so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.31,0:39:57.41,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I’ll test you. Here it comes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.91,0:40:05.02,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu-kun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.02,0:40:07.52,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,That was just luck, here I go!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.97,0:40:48.02,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Kaizu’s incredible!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.12,0:40:51.50,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is pathetic; he couldn’t return anything!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.31,0:40:57.01,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the match is over. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:59.01,0:41:00.26,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizu-kun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.20,0:41:07.24,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You remember calling me a loser?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:07.53,0:41:10.19,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes I do, of course!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.25,0:41:14.06,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I’m just a boring, spoiled girl.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.06,0:41:15.81,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ride in your car?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.01,0:41:17.40,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.79,0:41:21.77,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ryuuichi. Are you forgetting about me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.00,0:41:23.29,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:23.38,0:41:25.93,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He’s just not interested in old ladies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:25.93,0:41:27.56,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.59,0:41:31.80,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just joking. I can’t believe you took it seriously!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.12,0:41:35.59,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ryuuichi? I want to hear your feelings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.28,0:41:38.90,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You’re embarrassing yourself, senpai.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:38.90,0:41:41.48,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Please don’t look at me like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.48,0:41:44.56,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s true; I’ve lost interest in you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.76,0:41:48.26,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Ryuuichi-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.26,0:41:49.36,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.40,0:41:56.16,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do, captain? How can we allow this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.36,0:41:58.48,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Snap out of it, captain!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.48,0:42:01.01,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.33,0:42:07.65,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kaizu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.85,0:42:10.47,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize for what you said to Kuroeda!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.63,0:42:13.86,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Isn’t it a private matter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.16,0:42:17.91,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But I’m going to be frank...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.17,0:42:21.04,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,you have disrupted this Circle and we want you to quit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.41,0:42:23.49,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,We all discussed it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.80,0:42:28.16,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What’s so funny?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:28.34,0:42:30.92,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure are pleasant.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.92,0:42:35.90,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate me so much, why don’t you try to kick me out physically?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.90,0:42:38.56,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You discussed it? You make me laugh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.75,0:42:41.86,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,We aren’t animals; we deplore violence!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.38,0:42:44.79,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that’s the limit of people...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.79,0:42:47.05,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,who entertain themselves in a tennis circle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.28,0:42:48.71,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.20,0:42:52.50,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sick of you guys, satisfied to simply get into an elite school...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.75,0:42:56.85,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,satisfied to simply get a good job in a major company.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.48,0:43:00.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you losers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.72,0:43:03.19,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll quit this stupid circle on my own!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.36,0:43:05.85,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.00,0:43:09.97,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong? Come at me! You’re older, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:10.21,0:43:13.51,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,You’re gonna let a first year get away with THAT?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.79,0:43:17.89,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,There’s not a single guy with any guts among you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.95,0:43:19.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.81,0:43:25.73,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for the girls who enter here looking for boyfriends.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.75,0:43:30.72,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Sumibishi Hisayo-kun?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.72,0:43:34.57,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming, I’m sick of this trip too! Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.12,0:43:38.33,*Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hisayo-kun, not you too...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.33,0:43:44.62,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Later, this is goodbye. Future first-rate salarymen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:50.50,0:43:52.36,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,You’re gonna let him get away with that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.36,0:43:54.83,*Default,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a man, aren’t you? Do something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:55.03,0:43:56.88,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.07,0:44:04.83,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.35,0:44:07.42,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are amazing, Kaizu-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.42,0:44:09.01,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Not as much as you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:09.01,0:44:11.34,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I’m troublesome!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:11.34,0:44:15.00,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But now I’m away from my parents for a few days.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.00,0:44:17.74,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything I want. Take me somewhere!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.96,0:44:19.02,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.39,0:44:26.56,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you the car you want so don’t throw me away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.87,0:44:29.59,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t let anyone sit in this seat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.71,0:44:32.17,*Default,Sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be your slave or do whatever it takes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:33.26,0:44:36.39,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I promise.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.98,0:44:49.26,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn’t that the captain?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.71,0:44:54.19,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.19,0:44:56.25,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t lose to a guy like that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:17.08,0:45:18.84,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!! What an idiot!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:21.18,0:45:23.14,*Default,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Da... dammit!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.27,0:45:45.80,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I’m troublesome but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.80,0:45:47.26,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,But...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.53,0:45:51.29,*Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But please don’t think that I’d do this with just anyone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.81,0:45:54.76,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You’re the only one for me, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.07,0:46:06.74,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of my heart, blue flames burn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.63,0:46:12.46,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,I am not satisfied yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.88,0:46:17.69,*Default,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,As long as these flames burn, I will...
